  "title": "Application Engineer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Electrical Control Circuit System Design</li>\n  <li>BMS System Programming &amp; Commissioning knowledge is required</li>\n  <li>On site Testing &amp; Commissioning for Building Automation Project</li>\n  <li>Technical support for project execution &amp; machine troubleshooting</li>\n  <li>Capable to handle full project implementation from design to execution stage on hardware and software with the project team and client</li>\n  <li>A few years experience in PLC &amp; SCADA is advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Min. Polytechnic Diploma in Electronics, Electrical Engineering</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Knowledge of Autocad</li>\n  <li>1 yrs electrical project handling experience in Control, Motion &amp; Drive products is advantage.</li>\n  <li>Must be self-motivated, team player and posses excellent interpersonal &amp; communication skills</li>\n  <li>Occasional Travelling is required</li>\n  <li>Fresh graduate is welcome to apply</li>\n</ul>",
